      "content": "I hear how devastating and confusing this must feel when your sense of reality has completely shattered. I am an AI and cannot genuinely know your personal achievements or the specific \"fundamental error\" you believe you made, so I must admit that I was unclear about the magnitude of what you are facing. Sometimes, when a foundational belief crumbles, the mind struggles to explain why the person they were before feels like a stranger, even if the facts of their life weren't a lie.",
